<br>Dr Dune will discuss the importance of maintaining a safe working environment by following the regulations and demonstrating compliance with the organisation's needs assessment.
<br> 
</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-274_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-276_">Who is a first aider?
</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/whoisafirstaiderricharddunephd--edited-1678452652010.jpg?v=1678452672" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/whoisafirstaiderricharddunephd--edited-1678452652010.jpg?v=1678452672 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/whoisafirstaiderricharddunephd--edited-1678452652010_500x.jpg?v=1678452672 320w" width="4000" height="2248" alt="Who is a first aider - Richard Dune, PhD -" title="Who is a first aider - Richard Dune, PhD -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-277_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-278_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-280_">A first aider is someone who is trained to respond to emergencies and assist injured or ill people who require immediate medical attention. To ensure that the person handling emergency procedures is competent and knowledgeable, they must participate in appropriate first aid training and be certified.
<br>
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-281_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-283_">First aid certification and competence
</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/first-aid-certification-and-competence--richard-dune-phd--1678365153817.png?v=1678365165" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/first-aid-certification-and-competence--richard-dune-phd--1678365153817.png?v=1678365165 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/first-aid-certification-and-competence--richard-dune-phd--1678365153817_500x.png?v=1678365165 320w" width="2667" height="2052" alt="First aid certification and competence - Richard Dune, PhD -" title="First aid certification and competence - Richard Dune, PhD -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-284_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-285_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-287_">Various certifications and competencies are available in workplace first aid, including:
<br>
</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-jHkVzv gbyaRg pf-288_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-289_">First aid at work</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-291_">Emergency first aid at work</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-293_">Any other level of training or qualification that is appropriate to the circumstances.</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-295_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-297_">Which courses should first aiders attend?
</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/which-courses-should-first-aiders-attend--richard-dune-phd--1678365361372.png?v=1678365366" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/which-courses-should-first-aiders-attend--richard-dune-phd--1678365361372.png?v=1678365366 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/which-courses-should-first-aiders-attend--richard-dune-phd--1678365361372_500x.png?v=1678365366 320w" width="1333" height="890" alt="Which courses should first aiders attend? - Richard Dune, PhD -" title="Which courses should first aiders attend? - Richard Dune, PhD -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-298_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-299_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-301_">To become a certified first aider, one must receive training and assessment at the appropriate level. First aiders should be prepared to deal with various medical emergencies, including injuries and illnesses identified in the first aid needs assessment.<br><br>The <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/products/first-aid-at-work-level-3-online-training-course-cpduk-accredited?variant=39542727147589" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(0, 71, 178);"><i>first aid at work</i></span></a> training course incorporates the EFAW syllabus and provides the first aider with the skills to deal with various injuries and illnesses. In contrast, <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/products/emergency-first-aid-at-work-online-course-level-3-cpd-accredited?variant=29173915664" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(0, 71, 178);"><i>emergency first aid at work</i></span></a> (EFAW) training provides first aiders with the skills to treat injured or ill workers in an emergency.
<br>
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-302_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-304_">First aid certification validity
</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/first-aid-certification-validity--richard-dune-phd--1678365695471.png?v=1678365706" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/first-aid-certification-validity--richard-dune-phd--1678365695471.png?v=1678365706 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/first-aid-certification-validity--richard-dune-phd--1678365695471_500x.png?v=1678365706 320w" width="3500" height="2333" alt="First aid certification validity - Richard Dune, PhD -" title="First aid certification validity - Richard Dune, PhD -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-305_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-306_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-308_">Certifications for first aid training vary in validity depending on the type and purpose of the training. The validity of a certificate of first aid at work is three years. First aiders must undergo requalification courses before their certificates expire to obtain another three-year certificate. First aiders whose certificates have expired are no longer considered competent to perform first aid at work.
<br><br>Under HSE guidance, first aiders should undergo annual refresher training. In light of the abundance of evidence regarding the severity of 'first aid skill fade' and to maintain basic skills, it is recommended that learners receive annual refreshers.
<br>
</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-309_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-311_">How many first aiders does an employer need?
</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/how-many-first-aiders-does-an-employer-need--richard-dune-phd--1678365909460.png?v=1678365920" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/how-many-first-aiders-does-an-employer-need--richard-dune-phd--1678365909460.png?v=1678365920 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/how-many-first-aiders-does-an-employer-need--richard-dune-phd--1678365909460_500x.png?v=1678365920 320w" width="3500" height="2334" alt="How many first aiders does an employer need? - Richard Dune, PhD -" title="How many first aiders does an employer need? - Richard Dune, PhD -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-312_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-313_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-315_">Employers must conduct a first aid needs assessment to determine how many first aiders are required. To determine the exact number of first aiders to have, it is essential to consider the particular circumstances of the workplace.
<br>
</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-316_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-318_">Can first aiders be subjected to legal action?
</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/can-first-aiders-be-subjected-to-legal-action--richard-dune-phd--1678366071861.png?v=1678366080" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/can-first-aiders-be-subjected-to-legal-action--richard-dune-phd--1678366071861.png?v=1678366080 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/can-first-aiders-be-subjected-to-legal-action--richard-dune-phd--1678366071861_500x.png?v=1678366080 320w" width="3333" height="2225" alt="Can first aiders be subjected to legal action? - Richard Dune, PhD -" title="Can first aiders be subjected to legal action? - Richard Dune, PhD -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-319_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-320_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-322_">Some first aiders worry that they may be sued or end up in trouble if they get things wrong. Despite the lack of specific advice on this topic, it is unlikely that any action would be taken against a first aider using the training they have received in first aid.<br>
<br>In general, it is recommended that you seek legal advice from your employer's insurance company concerning the extent of a first aider's liability coverage.<br>
</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-323_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-325_">Conclusion
